		<title>뉴질랜드준비은행(RBNZ)의 매파적 인플레 발언에 상승하는 NZD/USD 환율</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/analysis/market-news/nzdusd-gains-hawkish-rbnz-inflation-comments</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 03:52:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[마켓 뉴스 및 자료]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[NZDUSD]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[최신 소식]]></category>
